        Hailey Baldwin has appeared to confirm that she and Justin Bieber are married by changing her Instagram name to Hailey Bieber.Justin also shared a picture of the pair together with the caption: "My wife is awesome."The 21-year-old model and the pop superstar were reported to have got married in secret in September.Hailey, who has 15.4 million followers, has changed both her handle and her bio.
    
        
