        There had been rumours that the couple had got married in a New York two months ago but Hailey denied it at the time.
    
        
She and Justin, who's 24, announced their engagement in July. Justin wrote on Instagram: "Hailey I am soooo in love with everything about you!"So committed to spending my life getting to know every single part of you loving you patiently and kindly."My heart is COMPLETELY and FULLY YOURS and I will ALWAYS put you first!"You are the love of my life Hailey Baldwin and I wouldn't want to spend it with anybody else." 
                
                
                
                
                
